Fetch updates origin/main
Merge updates main

git fetch = get latest changes from remote WITHOUT touching your work
✔️ Downloads changes
❌ Does NOT merge

git pull
Downloads changes
Automatically merges into your branch


🧠 Real-world analogy
clone → download full project (first time)
fetch → check for updates (like refreshing inbox)
pull → download + apply updates

memory trick
clone → “get the project”
fetch → “check for updates”
pull → “get + apply updates”

👉 git pull needs an existing repo

🧠 Final analogy (perfect)
clone → 🆕 install the app
pull → 🔄 update the app (download + install)
fetch → 📥 download update info (but don’t install)

👉 You can’t update something that isn’t installed yet

Real-life example

Think of your phone:

clone → install WhatsApp
fetch → check Play Store for updates
pull → update WhatsApp

👉 fetch = download updates without affecting your work
